File: Motorists can expect a healthy cut in the fuel price.  JOHANNESBURG - The petrol price will drop by 27 cents a litre at midnight.
Diesel will cost between 11 and 12 cents cheaper. READ: Are oil prices over the worst of the crisis? Paraffin users will, however, have to cough up between 15 and 20 cents more per litre. LP gas goes up by 26 cents a kilogram.